      "message": "What\u0027s bigger td.Patchset.{Host,Project} or td.Test?\n\nIf td.Patchset.{..}, then you could probably reduce RAM by re-using strings (i forgot name for this technique):\n\nknownStrings :\u003d map[strings]string\nfunc reuse(s string) string {\n  v, ok :\u003d knownStrings[s]\n  if ok { return v }\n  knownStrings[s] \u003d s\n  return s\n}\ntd.Patchset.Host \u003d reuse(td.Patchset.Host)\n\n\nUpdate: ah, but sadly the same is required with JSON, unless you read it semi-manually.",
